DEPENDENCIES
* google-sparsehash
  http://code.google.com/p/google-sparsehash/
* Boost C++ Libraries
* UnitTest++
* libconfig++
* sysv_ipc python package
  http://pypi.python.org/pypi/sysv_ipc

STYLE GUIDE
* We follow Google C++ Style Guide
  http://google-styleguide.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/cppguide.xml

SOURCE CODE OVERVIEW
src/dcc    distributed concurrency control
src/dpo    distributed persistent objects 
src/rpc    remote procedure call
src/mfs    memory file system backend
